            "href": "https://try.sanebox.com/dfa515mcau8s"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you're like me, you've spent too many hours sifting through newsletters, CCs, and low-priority emails. That's why I'm thrilled to dive into the new features of SaneBox, an AI-powered tool that acts like a personal email assistant. It automatically filters, prioritizes, and organizes your inbox, so you only see what truly matters. After using it for months, I've reclaimed at least 3-4 hours weekly—time I now spend on creative work or relaxing. Ready to transform your email experience? ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Discover SaneBox's magic",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and say goodbye to inbox chaos.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What's New: SaneBox's Latest Features to Supercharge Your Inbox",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "SaneBox continuously evolves, and its recent updates make email management even smarter. Here are the standout new features:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "SaneScreener",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": This feature acts as a gatekeeper for unknown senders. Instead of cluttering your inbox, emails from new contacts go into a screening folder, where you can quickly approve or block them. It's perfect for avoiding spam without missing important messages.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "SaneDrafts",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Ever forget to follow up on a draft? SaneDrafts reminds you about unfinished emails, ensuring nothing slips through the cracks. I've saved several client communications thanks to this nudge.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "SaneSummary",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": For heavy email users, this generates daily or weekly summaries of your email activity, highlighting key threads and actions needed. It's like having a briefing without the hassle.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-sanebox"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "These features build on SaneBox's core AI, which learns your habits over time. Whether you're using Gmail, Outlook, or Apple Mail, it integrates seamlessly—no downloads required. If you're curious about the full potential, ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "learn more about how SaneBox works",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How SaneBox's AI Works Like Your Personal Email Assistant",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "At its heart, SaneBox uses machine learning to analyze your email patterns. It looks at who you communicate with, what you open, and how you respond. Based on this, it automatically sorts emails into folders like @SaneLater for less urgent messages or keeps important ones in your inbox. For example, emails from your boss stay front and center, while newsletters get tucked away for your weekend read.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The AI adapts quickly—within a few days, it was accurately filtering my emails with over 90% accuracy. This isn't just filtering; it's intelligent prioritization. I no longer waste time deciding what to open first; SaneBox does it for me. It's like having a diligent assistant who knows your priorities inside out.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Key Features That Make SaneBox Stand Out",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Beyond the new additions, SaneBox's existing features are game-changers. Here's a breakdown of what I rely on daily:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "SaneLater",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Moves non-urgent emails to a dedicated folder, so your inbox stays focused. I check this folder once a day, saving countless interruptions.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "SaneNoReplies",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Tracks emails you've sent that haven't received a response, nudging you to follow up. This has helped me close deals faster and maintain client relationships.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "SaneDoNotDisturb",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Allows you to pause email notifications during deep work sessions. I use this for focused coding blocks, and it's boosted my productivity immensely.",
